  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Project Engineer (Mechanical)",
  "description": "<p>Our client is <strong>European MNC in Machinery Manufacturing.</strong> Due to business needs, they are now recruiting a <strong>Project Engineer </strong>to be part of their Team for ongoing transformation projects. They are located in the <strong>West Area.</strong></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Engage clients to gather, define, and confirm project requirements and specifications</li><li>Support in defining project scope and objectives, ensuring stakeholder alignment and technical feasibility.</li><li>Participate in project costing, risk assessment, and coordination of internal teams and external vendors</li><li>Develop and manage detailed project plans to track progress and ensure timely, within-scope, and within-budget delivery.</li><li>Control and manage changes to project scope, schedule, and costs using appropriate tools and verification methods.</li><li>Monitor project performance and evaluate progress against short- and long-term objectives.</li><li>Build and maintain strong relationships with third-party vendors and partners.</li><li>Maintain and ensure compliance with Quality Management System (QMS), ISO, and BizSafe standards</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Min Diploma in Mechanical Engineering </li><li>Experience in Project Management</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click APPLY NOW or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.<br /></p><p><strong>Email Address: </strong><a href=\"mailto:jobs@recruitpedia.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></a></p><p>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.</p><p>EA License No: 19C9682</p><p>EA Personnel No: R25157233 (Loh Pooi Keng)</p>",
